snippet.title: Will jail tame my wild teen daughter?
snippet.description:
It’s an episode of teens out of control on today’s Maury. 15 year old Caitlin’s mother, Jackie and step-father, Jason want to confront their daughter about her outrageous behavior! Caitlin is known to brag about her sexual experiences and Jackie has even heard her daughter make sexual advances toward a boy. The final straw was when Jackie walked into her bedroom and caught Caitlin and a boy having sex. Jackie and Jason are terrified that Caitlin may become a teen mom or worse contract a sexually transmitted disease that can changer her life forever.  Next, Albee says her now 13 year old daughter Sayla has always been a handful. Sayla says she’s been in 9 fights and proud to be undefeated! She also admits to stealing money, jewelry and expensive a Louis Vuitton hand bag from a family member. Psychotherapist Tom Kersting, HIV Activist Maria Meija and ex-con to icon Kail Muscle will lend a hand in hopes of getting through to these out of control teenage girls!
